---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Experience | Jeyson Andrés Mueses">
  <section class="animate">
    <span class="section-label" data-t="experience_label">[08] Experience</span>
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;" data-t="experience_title">Work Experience</h2>

    <div class="items-list">
      <div class="item" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 4px; padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
        <div class="item-header">
          <span style="font-weight: 500;">Data Analyst & BI Developer</span>
          <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary);">2023 — Present</span>
        </div>
        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Corporación Favorita · Quito, Ecuador</span>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.7;">Designing and maintaining the company's BI reporting infrastructure using Power BI and SQL Server. Built a centralized executive dashboard that replaced 12 separate Excel reports and reduced reporting cycle time from 4 days to 6 hours. Responsible for ETL pipeline development, data model design, and stakeholder training.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 4px; padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
        <div class="item-header">
          <span style="font-weight: 500;">Junior Data Analyst</span>
          <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary);">2022 — 2023</span>
        </div>
        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Banco Pichincha · Quito, Ecuador</span>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.7;">Supported the business intelligence team in building credit risk and customer segmentation reports. Wrote complex SQL queries against a SQL Server data warehouse with 500M+ records. Developed automated Python scripts for data quality validation, reducing manual QA effort by 70%.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 4px; padding: 16px 0;">
        <div class="item-header">
          <span style="font-weight: 500;">Data Analytics Intern</span>
          <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary);">2021 — 2022</span>
        </div>
        <span style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Freelance · Remote</span>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.7;">Delivered end-to-end data analysis projects for 4 SMEs across retail and logistics sectors. Designed Power BI dashboards for inventory tracking and sales performance monitoring. Introduced Looker Studio as a low-cost reporting alternative for clients without BI licenses.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
    <a href="/portfolio" class="nav-link" style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; text-decoration: none;" data-t="back_home"><i data-lucide="arrow-left"></i> Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
